px; WIDTH: 252pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">1-416-849-0833<font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\"><br>\n</font><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">Pass code:</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 216pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font>2760858</font></div>\n\n<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">Archived audio webcast:</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 252pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\"><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font>www.wheatonpm.com</font><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">&#160;</font></font></div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; TEXT-ALIGN: left\">Wheaton Precious Metals' quarterly reporting for the remainder of 2018 is scheduled to be issued, after market close, on the following dates:</div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\">\n<table id=\"zeffb3e4b40ca447bbbec6c0c56bee4cf\" class=\"DSPFListTable\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; WIDTH: 100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"WIDTH: 18pt\"></td>\n<td style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol, serif; WIDTH: 18pt; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top; align: right\">&#183;</td>\n<td style=\"WIDTH: auto; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top; TEXT-ALIGN: left\">\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">Q1 2018 &#8211; Thursday, May 10, 2018</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"TEXT-ALIG